<br>
Simple mathematics.... I know not your strong suit but please try to follow along.<br>
<br>
Guild A has 40 members.  They Kill mob X that drops 4 loots.  Each member of Guild A has 4/40 = 10% chance to get a loot.<br>
<br>
Guild B has 80 members.  They kill mob X that drops 4 loots.  Each member of Guild B has 4/80 = 5% chance to get loot.<br>
<br>
10% chance to get a loot is greater than 5% chance to get a loot.<br>
